Creating Relationship 10

Creating  Relationship between the tables in the Model View:

Follow the Screenshots to create the relationship.

Relationship 1

IMockInterviewCritique table to Date table - Many to One - Single - Active 


Relationship 2 -

IMockInterviewCritique table and Interviewer table - Many to One - Single - Inactive

Relationship 3.

Interviewer table  and Interviewee table - One to One - Both - Active

Relationship 4 -

IMockInterviewCritique table and Interviewee table - Many to One - Both - Active

Relationship 5

 Date table to Interviewer table  - One to Many  - Single - Inactive 


Relationship 6

 Date table to Interviewee table  - One to Many  - Single - Inactive 


This is the final one after creating all the relationships.


Making relationship in Power BI for reports:

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/transform-model/desktop-create-and-manage-relationships
